{"tid":671130,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"哈里王子大婚 卡尼被抽乾","createTime":"2018-05-20T01:34:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-20T02:31:13.000Z","uid":37875,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"7a6128be111aa13f19537f4e728e96fed739851a","tid":671130,"uid":37875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T01:34:07.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=JJx%2BhOoRaLnw80yk8FS4fdU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=c96e2b5a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】英國周六最大新聞就是哈里王子跟Meghan Markle成婚，想不到熱刺射手哈利卡尼躺著也中槍。<br />\n<br />\n自從為爭英超金靴獎把隊友基斯甸艾歷臣的入球，向英格蘭足總上訴「據為己有」後，哈利卡尼（Harry Kane）就成為了網民的抽水對象，可憐的是，這名英格蘭國腳最終也未能追過利物浦翼鋒穆罕默德沙拿。<br />\n<br />\n在哈里王子跟Meghan Markle成婚這天，不少網民都改圖抽卡尼水，把卡尼的樣貌key到哈里王子或Meghan身上，諷刺他會把新娘或新郎「據為己有」。<br />\n<br />\n不少網民的留言都非常抵死，有人說：「卡尼自稱跟Meghan在今天結婚。」也有人表示：「卡尼聲稱與Meghan結婚了沒有？還是他在等英足總的判決？」亦有人指：「我剛剛聽到消息，卡尼說自己編寫那結婚誓詞。」<br />\n<br />\n圖片來源 : Twitter圖片"},{"pid":"a72f83d7ea1fa4b5be9d61cff196a1922b0bd5e4","tid":671130,"uid":41423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T01:35:45.000Z","msg":"Megan 改姓Claim<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c49968770cf84406750f7a95f889d60691f0bf8","tid":671130,"uid":41423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a72f83d7ea1fa4b5be9d61cff196a1922b0bd5e4","tid":671130,"uid":41423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T01:35:45.000Z","msg":"Megan 改姓Claim<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T01:36:08.000Z","msg":"Meghan"},{"pid":"aa28b620b7529eed5b0c6c939e78a2a0d8d7889a","tid":671130,"uid":161311,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T01:41:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/20/094117_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%